ackground-color:#f9fafb;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:4px;line-height:1.6;\"><strong>At TP1 ($55):</strong> 4 shares × $55 = $220 gross | Gross gain: ($55−$41.7755)×4 = +$52.90 | −$3 exit = <strong style=\"color:#059669;\">+$49.90 net ✅</strong><br><strong>At stop ($38):</strong> 8 shares × $38 = $304 gross | Loss: $304−$334.20−$3 = <strong style=\"color:#dc2626;\">−$33.20 net</strong>. Stop at $38 is valid market structure (pre-catalyst base).</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:8px;background-color:#f0fdf4;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px;\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td><span style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#374151;\">ANET</span> <span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;\">Arista Networks — EXITED</span> <span style=\"margin-left:8px;padding:2px 8px;background-color:#059669;color:#fff;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;\">✅ TP HIT +15.8%</span></td>\n          <td align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#059669;\">+$31.56 net</span></td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n      <p style=\"margin:10px 0 6px 0;font-size:13px;color:#065f46;\">Limit sell at $185 <strong>confirmed executed July 9, 2026.</strong> Stock hit intraday ATH of $189.82 — order filled at $185 or better. Closed Jul 10 at $186.96, confirming the level held.</p>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;background-color:#dcfce7;border-radius:4px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Gross P&amp;L: (185 − 157.7874) × 1.27 = <strong>+$34.56</strong></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Exit commission: <strong>−$3.00</strong></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;border-top:1px solid #bbf7d